script: You will be given three messages from different people Rohan Davey, Laura Anderson, and Rowan Keaney.
Laura Anderson: The time we will meet is when the moon is high.
Rohan Davey: Bring to the meeting a way to persuade the border guards to let us through.
Rowan Keaney: We will rendezvous where the sea cargo is stored.
Given the clandestine messages you have received, tell me as specifically as you can, when and where the meeting is going to happen and what you should bring.
